snippet.title: MaWhoo, GL_Ceejay and Thukuthela - Bengicela [Feat. Jazzworx] (Official Audio)
snippet.description:
MaWhoo, GL_Ceejay and Thukuthela present the official audio to Bengicela featuring Jazzworx.

After the outstanding success of “Uzizwa Kanjan,” acclaimed South African songstress MaWhoo has teamed up with GL_Ceejay, Thukuthela and Jazzworx again for her latest single “Bengicela.” The anthemic track is an earnest prayer. It’s a plea to be heard by a Higher Power. 

“This song comes as a plea for God’s mercy & wisdom. There is so much going on in the world we live in. All I pray for is for God to hear us and all of our cries. We made the song with Jazzworx, Thukuthela and GL_Ceejay, right after making Uzizwa Kanjani,” shares MaWhoo.

[Intro - Thukuthela]

Aaahh Bawo, Wuwe wedwa ohlezi odal’ iy’manga
